query:
SELECT
                COUNT(*) as auction_count,
                COALESCE(SUM(CAST(buy_cost_token AS NUMERIC)), 0)::TEXT as total_spend,
                MAX(time_bought) as latest_time_bought
            FROM land_historical
            WHERE owner = $1
              AND buy_token_used IS NULL
              AND time_bought >= $2
              AND time_bought < $3
